Class Lep

java.lang.Object
pkgMain.Lep
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Lep
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
The Lep class represents a lep, lepidoptera, that can be supported by a plant.
